Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 未来露西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才一天 怎么可能填补实力的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有夏·多拉格尼尔那么厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Comment: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,==========Main==========
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候到来之前 我们一直待在牢里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…露西为什么会从未来过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了改变最糟糕的未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最糟糕的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底…你所在的未来发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在前方等着我们的是绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有超过一万头龙的龙群袭击这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,街道被烧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城市开始崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许多人失去了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:07.87,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(640,450)\fad(524,0}转变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超过一万头龙的龙群…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些话…我无法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到看到大魔斗比武的结果 我都不会相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什？ 么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超过一万头龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会发生这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道和那个龙之墓场有关么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出大事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们是从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能没有任何风声就潜进来的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之不能干等着 要做战前准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要迎战吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不过的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都相信我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是骗人的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为这种事情不会有人相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要怀疑露西说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来的我还真是这么没出息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要信任自己的同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在对自己说教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就说通了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崩坏的城堡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱歌…不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在哭喊的露西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个龙群来袭的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样在城堡中的我们怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏露露 别追问了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们大概是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都死掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为和我在一起吗 所以才会不走运
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道过了多少天了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我醒过来后 想起来了关于日蚀的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道启动方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是在忘我地时候打开了大门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并盲目地相信这样也许可以回到过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我就真的回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到了791年7月4日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是最近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日蚀只能回到这么近的过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 回到400年前打倒泽雷夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:07:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是因为当时日蚀有一部分已经坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向公主进言的神秘未来人就是这个家伙么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 令人在意的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,街上都是为大魔斗比武摄影的魔水晶屏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想从地下走和杰拉尔他们汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰拉尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把一切都和他坦白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 他应该在思考对策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在思考对策？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没能从未来带来解决这件事的对策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道怎样才能避免那种局势的发生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从…从未来来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:07:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人告诉了我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日蚀的另一种使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日蚀2
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2？ 那到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这7年间我们利用大魔斗比武
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为这扇门积累了不少魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过这种方法收集的魔力可以和魔法精灵力相媲美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…竟然可以和魔法评议院拥有的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说可以毁灭一个国家的神圣之光媲美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将这个力量向龙群发射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是日蚀2计划
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经向公主建议使用日蚀2
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所说的回到了4日前根本就是谎话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要欺骗自己的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常对不起 这样一来我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不知道自己是为什么而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前我一直不知道该怎么办才好 只是在街上晃来晃去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我们一定会想出办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 为了我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会扭转未来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一定全是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说未来的露西可能在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么特地…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:09:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超过一万条龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日蚀…魔力…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一些前后矛盾的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她故意混乱于未来有关的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是露西在说谎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说那个露西本身就是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.24,0:10:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙敢再说一遍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁没强到谁那种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗格…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉我渐渐明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会加入妖精的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也怪你不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:10:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那时侯还是个光头小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憧憬着你所在的协会幽鬼支配者的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我长大以后可以加入幽鬼支配者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 它却在和妖精尾巴的战争中败北
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协会也解散了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅如此 你还加入了可恶的妖精尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时无法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偏偏要加入击溃幽鬼的协会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你加入妖精尾巴一定是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑咬之虎就没有这样的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是会长的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要绝对服从命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜利才是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是协会 就应该珍惜同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协会是什么…同伴又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底是为了什么在战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在终于知道你们为何如此强大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赢不了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过过分强大的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和因为雷克特而觉醒的斯汀可能算是例外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本就什么都没明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只青蛙是你的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青蛙？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛是只猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正确的说是超越者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 弗洛是我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢不了你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人仍然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然站在你面前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁 是谁在说话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗格…杀掉伽吉鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:13:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是你的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我借给你力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉伽吉鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏你知道这种路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少想要避免掉大家被王国军抓住的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下都调查好了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想早点发射信号弹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也一定很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王国军？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会安排在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 能用魔法就不会被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁卡迪欧斯不见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃也不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要擅自这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不说那个骑士 我们不能放着雪乃不管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去找
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不能分开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧 我们要把这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突破掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米拉小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱来保护夏露露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种不安的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 突然间怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉伽吉鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 我的命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我借给你力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽吉鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然间怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是说了什么比较在意的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就稍微借给你一点力量吧 罗格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是掌管命运的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正就是要尽情打是吧 有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 刚不是还要和解呢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉情况有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽吉鲁 要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁龙剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影龙的连雀闪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽吉鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗格？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影龙的斩击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初代 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是被什么附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊 刚刚变成影子也还能抓到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力的质变了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常 非常邪恶的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的知识中不存在的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然没有夏·多拉格尼尔那样厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个夏·多拉格尼尔也打不过现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个魔力…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在城镇方向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静 未来露西被卷进战斗中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有夏他们在就不必慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退下 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙明明是小鬼 怎么这么强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼唤对魔法部队
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让他们从这里过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备第二波第三波
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家也有魔法部队？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓我一跳 就用这种魔法和专业的打？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没效果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小鬼是怪物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 久等了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没在等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别擅自出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？ 费欧雷王国最强的魔法兵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太盛大啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法师吗？ 不是星灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那样的星灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要调教呢 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了美丽的翡翠公主 让我好好活跃一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把同伴也卷进来？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怕的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各种意义上都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力气还挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体力我还挺有自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是能伸长？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思…不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 自称是最强我们就尽全力上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 看我把你的全力挡下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龙的铁拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是那个伽吉鲁吗 丢死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 他会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽吉鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛必须要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得让他把罗格还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子会侵蚀你 然后你会永远消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在黑暗中沉眠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龙神能做到 我没道理做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把影子…吃掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起 真做出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸收了影的属性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你快滚出那家伙的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从罗格？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 他的名字不叫罗格
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我的小弟莱欧斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是憧憬我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:22:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候我不是那样的人 我自己最清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是害怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就再让你回想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.97,0:22:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的恐怖之处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁影龙？！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========Preview==========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:24:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？ 伽吉鲁那家伙把影子吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.12,0:24:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有资格说别人么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏还不是能吃火
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子和火不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.13,0:24:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火是食物 而且很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说确实是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.22,0:24:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还这不理解有人居然能吃影子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱对你们这种类型的都看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.72,0:24:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 激雷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.47,0:24:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我就推荐点好吃的火给哈比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.77,0:24:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 这就算了
